{
  "text": "\u03c4 independently from Laplace(0, 1), and setting jk = U j Z jk / \u221a 2, where U j is the lower triangle Cholesky decomposition of V j . The MN and MT settings are the same as those used in [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] and [CITATION_3] .",
  "correct_citation": {
